         <abstract id="aspace_1a95832bcdca6a701df59d8c9fcc3c92">The records consist of memoranda, correspondence, notes, drawings, specifications, and awards documenting Roth and Moore Architects' design and construction of the Seeley G. Mudd Library, Yale University.</abstract>
